NODEJS:
1) nodejs -> https://nodejs.org/en/
a) dowload the latest stable  version

ANGULAR
1) npm install -g @angular/cli

CREATE NEW ANGULAR PROJECT:
1) ng new project-name

OPEN THE SERVER:
- ng serve
- open the browser to localhost:4200


ADD ANGULAR MATERIAL:
ng add @angular/material


EXPRESS
npm install --save express

NODEMON
a) npm i --save-dev nodemon
b) go to package.json and under the scripts, add "start:server": "nodemon server.js"
c) add an import to the server.js. const debug = require("debug")("node-angular");
d) in your terminal type: npm run start:server

BODY PARSER
a) npm i --save body-parser
b) add an import to the app.js. const bodyParser = require("body-parser");

